Call Ronnie at OldVolks/Type 2 parts and order a Freeway Flyer tranny.  My
FF has a 3.88 R&P and WITH reduction boxes, I have had it up to 81-82 miles
per hour.  I am running a 1600DP and the ~81 MPH was going down hill, but it
is very possible with RGB's.

Bryant


